.TH DAIFUPDOWN 1 "2026-01-02" "dumbass-tree" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
daifupdown \- ifupdown migration helper (generate interfaces, disable netplan YAML)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B daifupdown
[--dry-run] [-v] <command>
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B plan
Inspect netplan YAML, active services, resolv.conf wiring, and interfaces.
.TP
.B generate
Generate /etc/network/interfaces content based on live interfaces (stdout by default).
.TP
.B generate --write
Write /etc/network/interfaces with backup + two-tier warning.
.TP
.B disable-netplan
Move /etc/netplan/*.yaml aside (disable netplan config) with two-tier warning.
